author: Brad Brooks
title: In Texas, a coastal city tries to test its way out of coronavirus pandemic
description: Each day, hundreds of residents of Galveston County, Texas, are tested for the new coronavirus. Free diagnostic tests are being offered to anyone over the age of seven and the county has enough test kits to last a month.
content:
